00:35:59.615 --> 00:36:00.867
Siento decirte esto,

00:36:01.826 --> 00:36:03.536
pero no has destruido a nadie.

00:36:05.329 --> 00:36:06.873
Gu-won ha vuelto

00:36:07.874 --> 00:36:09.750
